Title: Ice-Watch 38mm Forest urban grey FT UGY S S 14
Description: chapelle_jewellery Visit our eBay Shop Add us to your Favourites list > Subscribe to our Newsletter > About Chapelle Delivery The Chapelle Guarantee Ice-Watch 38mm Forest urban grey FT UGY S S 14 RRP £69.95 Now £44.95 Description This designer watch by Ice is part of the Forest collection, which all have a sporty design, but with dark neutral colours. The dial of this watch is 38 mm in width, and is a good size for both men and women. As this FOREST watch is made of silicone, the strap is waterproof and is suitable for you to work out in. The dial is 100 metres water resistant meaning that you can swim, dive and go snorkelling in this Ice-Watch. With the Ice-FOREST collection, the entire watch is one colour, bar the hour and minute hand, the tip of the second hand, and the ‘Ice’ logo that is situated to the right of the dial. This particular watch is entirely a dark forest green, except for the aforementioned features which are white. The white accents stand out well against the darker background, but also have a modern look to it. At Chapelle Jewellery the watches are all 30% off RRP- if not more.
